---
layout: base.njk
title: "The Afro Groove Library | The Groove Library"
description: >
  <p>Rooted in music from and inspired by Africa, this series explores rhythm as both heritage and evolution — moving between traditional forms, vintage recordings, modern productions, edits, fusions and underground mutations.</p>

  <p>Across DJ mixes, live sessions, guest selectors and deep listening experiences, The Afro Groove Library traces connections between highlife, Afro-funk, desert blues, spiritual jazz, dub, house, broken beat, electronic experiments and everything in-between. It honours the source while embracing forward motion.</p>

  <p>This is not a museum of sound — it's a living archive. Built for dancers, listeners, collectors and curious minds. Equal parts ritual, system culture and future exploration.</p>

  <p>Where the roots run deep… and the groove keeps moving.</p>
playlist: "the-afro-groove-library"
---

{# Hero Section #}
<section class="region region--lg bg-brand" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="center center--intrinsic flow flow--lg text-center">
      <div class="flow flow--md">
        <h1 id="hero-heading" class="text-4xl text-inverse">
          The Afro Groove Library
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-inverse mx-auto">
          Rhythm as heritage and evolution — Africa-rooted, globally connected.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cluster cluster--md justify-center">
        <fa-icon icon="globe-africa" size="2x" class="text-inverse" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
        <fa-icon icon="drum" size="2x" class="text-inverse" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
        <fa-icon icon="compact-disc" size="2x" class="text-inverse" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Description Section #}
{% if description %}
<section class="region region--lg" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="wrapper wrapper--narrow flow">
      {{ description | safe }}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{# Mix Collection Section #}
<section class="region region--xl" aria-labelledby="mixes-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="flow flow--xl">
      {# Section Header #}
      <div class="flow flow--sm text-center">
        <h2 id="mixes-heading" class="text-3xl">
          The Collection
        </h2>

        {% if theAfroGrooveLibrary.count > 0 %}
          <div class="cluster cluster--sm justify-center">
            <span class="badge">
              <fa-icon icon="record-vinyl" size="sm" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
              {{ theAfroGrooveLibrary.count }} mixes in this collection
            </span>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      {# Mix Grid #}
      {% if theAfroGrooveLibrary.cloudcasts.length > 0 %}
        <div class="grid grid--2" role="list" aria-label="The Afro Groove Library mixes">
          {% for mix in theAfroGrooveLibrary.cloudcasts %}
            <div role="listitem">
              {% include "mix-player.njk" %}
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      {% elif theAfroGrooveLibrary.error %}
        {# Error State #}
        <div class="error" role="alert">
          <h3 class="error__title">
            <fa-icon icon="triangle-exclamation" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
            Unable to load mixes
          </h3>
          <p>We encountered an error while fetching the music collection. Please try again later.</p>
          <details class="my-md">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-semibold">Technical details</summary>
            <p class="text-sm my-sm"><code>{{ theAfroGrooveLibrary.error }}</code></p>
          </details>
        </div>
      {% else %}
        {# Empty State #}
        <div class="center center--intrinsic flow flow--lg text-center py-3xl">
          <fa-icon icon="music-slash" size="4x" class="text-tertiary" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
          <div class="flow flow--sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl">No mixes available</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary">Check back soon for new content!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
